        description: "Transposing is one of those musical skills that sounds complicated but is surprisingly straightforward " \
        "once you understand the basics."
      },
      {
        title: "Chordly User Guide", id: "guide-to-using-chordly", image: "/article_assets/library.png",
        description: "Chordly is designed to make creating and managing chord sheets as simple as possible. This short guide " \
        "will walk you through the main features so you can get started quickly."
      },
      {
        title: "Putting Together a Set List for Your Next Gig", id: "tips-for-your-setlist",
        image: "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/83/Musicians_at_Velour_Live_Music_Gallery_%28Unsplash%2" \
        "9.jpg/640px-Musicians_at_Velour_Live_Music_Gallery_%28Unsplash%29.jpg",
        description: "A great set list is more than just a list of songs—it's the roadmap for your performance, shaping the " \
        "audience's energy and keeping your band on track. Whether you're preparing..."
